@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/class-diagram
' 实验二：工厂模式与敌机攻击
' 开发目标：
' ① UML 类图设计 - 简单工厂模式与工厂方法模式
' ② 设计模式应用 - 简单工厂实现道具创建，工厂方法实现敌机创建
' ③ 敌机生成 - 4 种敌机按周期随机出现
' ④ 敌机移动 - 精锐和王牌可左右移动
' ⑤ 敌机攻击 - 精锐双排子弹，王牌扇形散射
' ⑥ 道具生成 - 击毁时概率掉落
' ⑦ 道具效果 - 控制台输出提示

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

' ==================== 基础抽象类 ====================
abstract class AbstractFlyingObject
{
    # locationX: int
    # locationY: int
    # speedX: int
    # speedY: int
    # image: BufferedImage
    # isValid: boolean
    
    + AbstractFlyingObject(int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + crash(AbstractFlyingObject): boolean
    + getLocationX(): int
    + getLocationY(): int
    + notValid(): boolean
    + vanish(): void
}

abstract class AbstractAircraft
{
    # hp: int
    # maxHp: int
    # power: int
    # score: int
    
    + AbstractAircraft(int, int, int, int, int)
    + decreaseHp(int): void
    + getHp(): int
    + getScore(): int
    + {abstract} shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
    + {abstract} forward(): void
}

abstract class BaseBullet
{
    # power: int
    
    + BaseBullet(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + getPower(): int
}

abstract class AbstractItem
{
    # speedY: int
    
    + AbstractItem(int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + {abstract} applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

' ==================== 英雄飞机 ====================
class HeroAircraft
{
    - shootNum: int
    - power: int
    - direction: int
    
    + HeroAircraft(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
}

' ==================== 敌机体系 ====================
abstract class AbstractEnemy
{
    + {abstract} dropSupply(): List<AbstractItem>
}

class MobEnemy
{
    + MobEnemy(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
    + dropSupply(): List<AbstractItem>
}

class EliteEnemy
{
    + EliteEnemy(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
    + dropSupply(): List<AbstractItem>
}

class AceEnemy
{
    + AceEnemy(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
    + dropSupply(): List<AbstractItem>
}

class MasterEnemy
{
    + MasterEnemy(int, int, int, int, int)
    + forward(): void
    + shoot(): List<BaseBullet>
    + dropSupply(): List<AbstractItem>
}

note right of MasterEnemy
  **精锐敌机**
  - 左右移动
  - 双排子弹
  - 掉落 4 种道具
end note

note right of AceEnemy
  **王牌敌机**
  - 左右移动
  - 扇形散射 (3 发)
  - 掉落 5 种道具
end note

' ==================== 子弹体系 ====================
class HeroBullet
{
    + HeroBullet(int, int, int, int, int)
}

class EnemyBullet
{
    + EnemyBullet(int, int, int, int, int)
}

' ==================== 道具体系 ====================
class BloodItem
{
    + BloodItem(int, int, int)
    + applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

class BulletItem
{
    + BulletItem(int, int, int)
    + applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

class BulletPlusItem
{
    + BulletPlusItem(int, int, int)
    + applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

class BombItem
{
    + BombItem(int, int, int)
    + applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

class FreezeItem
{
    + FreezeItem(int, int, int)
    + applyEffect(HeroAircraft): void
}

enum ItemType
{
    BLOOD
    BOMB
    BULLET
    BULLET_PLUS
    FREEZE
}

note bottom of ItemType
  5 种道具类型
end note

' ==================== 单例模式 ====================
class HeroAircraftCreate
{
    - instance: HeroAircraftCreate
    - heroAircraft: HeroAircraft
    
    - HeroAircraftCreate()
    + getInstance(): HeroAircraftCreate
    + createHero(): void
    + getHero(): HeroAircraft
    + clear(): void
}

note right of HeroAircraftCreate
  **单例模式**
  懒汉式 + 双重检查锁
end note

' ==================== 简单工厂模式 - 道具 ====================
class ItemFactory
{
    - random: Random
    
    + createItem(ItemType type, int x, int y): AbstractItem
    + createRandomItem(ItemType[] types, int x, int y): AbstractItem
}

note right of ItemFactory
  **简单工厂模式**
  
  根据 ItemType 枚举
  创建对应道具对象
  
  优点：
  - 客户端无需知道
    具体产品类
  - 集中管理创建逻辑
end note

' ==================== 工厂方法模式 - 敌机 ====================
class EnemyFactory
{
    - random: Random
    - NORMAL_ENEMY_TYPES: EnemyAircraftType[]
    
    + createEnemy(EnemyAircraftType type): AbstractEnemy
    + createRandomNormalEnemy(): AbstractEnemy
}

enum EnemyAircraftType
{
    MOB
    ELITE
    ACE
    MASTER
}

note right of EnemyFactory
  **工厂方法模式**
  
  根据 EnemyAircraftType
  创建对应敌机对象
  
  优点：
  - 符合开闭原则
  - 易于扩展新敌机
end note

' ==================== 应用层 ====================
class Game
{
    - heroAircraft: HeroAircraft
    - enemyAircrafts: List<AbstractEnemy>
    - heroBullets: List<BaseBullet>
    - enemyBullets: List<BaseBullet>
    - enemyMaxNumber: int
    - enemySpawnCycle: double
    - shootCycle: double
    - score: int
    
    + Game()
    + action(): void
    - tick(): void
    - spawnEnemy(): void
    - shootAction(): void
    - bulletsMoveAction(): void
    - aircraftMoveAction(): void
    - crashCheckAction(): void
    - checkHeroBulletHit(): void
    - checkItemPickup(): void
    - postProcessAction(): void
    - render(): void
}

class Main
{
    + WINDOW_WIDTH: int
    + WINDOW_HEIGHT: int
    + main(String[] args): void
}

class ImageManager
{
    + BACKGROUND_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + HERO_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + MOB_ENEMY_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + ELITE_ENEMY_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + ACE_ENEMY_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + MASTER_ENEMY_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + HERO_BULLET_IMAGE: BufferedImage
    + ENEMY_BULLET_IMAGE: BufferedImage
}

class HeroController
{
    + HeroController(Game game, HeroAircraft hero)
}

' ==================== 继承关系 ====================
AbstractFlyingObject <|-- AbstractAircraft
AbstractFlyingObject <|-- BaseBullet
AbstractFlyingObject <|-- AbstractItem

AbstractAircraft <|-- HeroAircraft
AbstractAircraft <|-- AbstractEnemy

AbstractEnemy <|-- MobEnemy
AbstractEnemy <|-- EliteEnemy
AbstractEnemy <|-- AceEnemy
AbstractEnemy <|-- MasterEnemy

BaseBullet <|-- HeroBullet
BaseBullet <|-- EnemyBullet

AbstractItem <|-- BloodItem
AbstractItem <|-- BulletItem
AbstractItem <|-- BulletPlusItem
AbstractItem <|-- BombItem
AbstractItem <|-- FreezeItem

' ==================== 模式关系 ====================
HeroAircraftCreate o-- HeroAircraft : creates >

ItemFactory ..> AbstractItem : creates >
ItemFactory ..> ItemType : uses >

EnemyFactory ..> AbstractEnemy : creates >
EnemyFactory ..> EnemyAircraftType : uses >

' ==================== 关联关系 ====================
Game o-- HeroAircraft : controls >
Game o-- AbstractEnemy : manages >
Game o-- BaseBullet : manages >
Game o-- AbstractItem : manages >

Game ..> EnemyFactory : uses >
Game ..> ItemFactory : uses >

Main ..> Game : starts >
HeroController ..> HeroAircraft : controls >

' ==================== 注释说明 ====================
note bottom of Game
  **游戏主循环**
  
  - 敌机生成 (工厂方法)
  - 敌机射击 (精英/精锐/王牌)
  - 道具掉落 (简单工厂)
  - 碰撞检测
  - 道具拾取
end note

note bottom of AbstractEnemy
  **4 种敌机特性**
  
  MobEnemy: 普通敌机，不射击
  EliteEnemy: 精英敌机，单排子弹
  MasterEnemy: 精锐敌机，双排子弹，左右移动
  AceEnemy: 王牌敌机，扇形散射，左右移动
end note

note bottom of AbstractItem
  **道具效果**
  
  BloodItem: 恢复 50 血量
  BulletItem: 火力升级，打印提示
  BulletPlusItem: 超级火力，打印提示
  BombItem: 清除敌机，打印提示
  FreezeItem: 冻结敌机，打印提示
end note

note right of Game
  **敌机生成逻辑**
  
  - 按周期随机生成
  - 4 种类型随机选择
  - 最大数量限制
  - 不包含 Boss
end note

@enduml
